        {
            "id": 6007940,
            "title": "主動式ETF加入戰局！台股ETF受益人寫新高 00919、00878等9檔同創高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據集保戶股權分散 5 月 29 日最新統計資料顯示，受到上周新增一檔主動統一台股增長 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00981A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00981A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981A-TW</a>) 的助益，整體受益人數上周增加 28448 人，台股 ETF 受益人數呈現連續 2 周成長，總人數來到 1113 萬 3766 人，創下歷史新高，總檔數也來到 73 檔，今年來增加 90 萬 7930 人。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007940%2Fl%2F97a0da1003565b735f538fe0192cf106.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">主動式ETF加入戰局！台股ETF受益人寫新高 00919、00878等9檔同創高。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>進一步觀察單檔表現，有 9 檔受益人同步創下新高，分別是群益台灣精選高息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00919:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00919-TW</a>)、元大台灣 50(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:0050:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/0050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">0050-TW</a>)、國泰永續高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00878:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00878-TW</a>)、元大台灣高息低波 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00713:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00713\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00713-TW</a>)、國泰臺灣加權反 1(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00664R:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00664R\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00664R-TW</a>)、國泰臺灣加權正 2(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00663L:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00663L\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00663L-TW</a>)，加上三檔主動式的主動群益台灣強棒 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00982A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00982A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00982A-TW</a>)、主動野村臺灣優選 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00980A:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00980A\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00980A-TW</a>)、00981A。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>整體來看，高息型與主動式相對受投資人青睞。其中，00919 最新公告第 9 次配息金額 0.72 元，預估年化配息率 12.98% 最高，也是在降息風中唯一逆勢配息維持新高的台股高息 ETF，00919 除息日為 6 月 17 日，參與除息最後買進日為 6 月 16 日，配息發放日 7 月 11 日，有興趣的投資人可多留意。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"450\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.6888888888888889\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007940/m/9eab387360c7bf7d6913a084edbacf42.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6007940/l/9eab387360c7bf7d6913a084edbacf42.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>群益台灣精選高息 ETF 經理人謝明志強調，在川普關稅邊際效應遞減，轉折時間點來臨，建議資產配置轉進積極與抗波動化並存，台股高息 ETF 有股息、又有潛在的價差空間可期，除了適合長期投資外，更是愛好存股領息的存股族投資人，參與台股投資的好選擇。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>群益台灣精選強棒主動式 ETF 經理人陳沅易表示，台股短線在端午連假與繳稅壓力下震盪整理難免，但長期在匯率、外資回補潛能、以及中小型題材股輪動活躍，為市場注入活水。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>操作上，陳沅易建議投資人聚焦籌碼集中、具產業題材及法人進駐的個股，善用震盪整理期佈局未來潛力股，以迎接節後行情回溫的契機。市場短期雜音不改長線多頭格局，投資人應秉持謹慎樂觀態度審慎應對。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
